content.rendered:
LPN | Tulsa, Oklahoma
  • Full-time, 3pm-11pm
  • will be responsible assisting patients with medication, documenting and other duties as needed
  • 1+ year LPN experience
  • Must have current LPN license in good standing
  • $20+/hour
